                                 oOoOoOoOoOo

  ABSTRACT:  Welcome to "Blob Kombat", a simple, yet addictive, game which
  ~~~~~~~~   requires only one or two friends and an AMIGA 1200. We hope you
  will have as much fun playing this game as we did creating it during the 
  long, hot summer of 1995.

                                 oOoOoOoOoOo

  SHAREWARE MESSAGE: This version of Blob Kombat is only a demo. The full
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~  version cost only six pounds to buy and features...

  o Twenty levels of multi-player mayhem
  o Some graphical embellishments
  o A level editor
  o A copy of the BLITZ 2 source code
